\begin_inset Formula \[
b=\ln 2-0.5\times 2=\ln 2-1\cong -0.306.\]

\end_inset 

We therefore have the equation 
\begin_inset Formula \[
y=0.5x-\ln 2+1.\]

\end_inset 


